        "calloutText": "<strong><em>Share this article on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Chicago%E2%80%99s%20mayoral%20aspirant%20enriched%20banks%20and%20helped%20create%20a%20financial%20crisis%20for%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20fourth%20largest%20school%20system.%20From%20%40matthewccook5.%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levernews.com%2Fhow-vallas-helped-wall-street-loot-chicagos-schools%2F%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dlink%26utm_campaign%3Dtw-prefill%20\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levernews.com%2Fhow-vallas-helped-wall-street-loot-chicagos-schools%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dlink%26utm_campaign%3Dfb-article&amp;amp;src=sdkpreparse\">Facebook</a></em></strong>.",
